rusMusic Player 22 (Linux)

rusMusic Player 22 (Linux)

January 2, 2000 - Ivan Ivanenko

Support for CUE (also wv, iso.wv) is the best under Linux (zavlab) Formats MP3, MP4, AAC, CD Audio, WMA, Vorbis, FLAC, WavPack, WAV, AIFF, Musepack, Speex, AU, SND ... Converter any format to any (mp3, ogg, mp2, ac3, m4a, wav) Scrobbler tags with music and radio Find and play music and videos Equalizer
